'''蹄蝠屬'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Hipposideros''}}），为[[哺乳綱|哺乳綱]]、[[翼手目|翼手目]]、[[菊頭蝠科|菊頭蝠科]]的一屬[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]。

==下属物种==
* [[宽袍蹄蝠|宽袍蹄蝠]] (阿巴蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros abae'' (Aba roundleaf bat)
* [[大蹄蝠|大蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros armiger'' (Great roundleaf bat)
* [[黑蹄蝠|黑蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros ater'' (Dusky roundleaf bat)
* [[侏蹄蝠|侏蹄蝠]] (西非小蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros beatus'' (Benito roundleaf bat)
* [[双色蹄蝠|双色蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros bicolor'' (Bicolored roundleaf bat)
* [[短颅蹄蝠|短颅蹄蝠]] (短頭蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros breviceps'' (Short-headed roundleaf bat)
* [[南非蹄蝠|南非蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros caffer'' (Sundevall's roundleaf bat)
* [[距蹄蝠|距蹄蝠]] (靴刺蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros calcaratus'' (Spurred roundleaf bat)
* [[喀麦隆蹄蝠|喀麦隆蹄蝠]] (大圓面蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros camerunensis'' (Greater roundleaf bat)
* [[澳洲蹄蝠|澳洲蹄蝠]] (黃褐蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros cervinus'' (Fawn roundleaf bat)
* [[小蹄蝠|小蹄蝠]] (灰蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros cineraceus'' (Ashy roundleaf bat)
* [[康氏蹄蝠|康氏蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros commersoni'' (Commerson's roundleaf bat)
* [[戴帽蹄蝠|戴帽蹄蝠]] (有冠蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros coronatus'' (Large Mindanao roundleaf bat)
* [[新几内亚蹄蝠|新几内亚蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros corynophyllus'' (Telefomin roundleaf bat)
* [[考氏蹄蝠|考氏蹄蝠]] (柯氏蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros coxi'' (Cox's roundleaf bat)
* [[帝汶蹄蝠|帝汶蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros crumeniferus'' (Timor roundleaf bat)
* [[短尾蹄蝠|短尾蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros curtus'' (Short-tailed roundleaf bat)
* [[大眼蹄蝠|大眼蹄蝠]] (圓面蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros cyclops'' (Cyclops roundleaf bat)
* [[冕蹄蝠|冕蹄蝠]] (帽盔蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros diadema'' (Diadem roundleaf bat)
* [[猛蹄蝠|猛蹄蝠]] (恐面蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros dinops'' (Fierce roundleaf bat)
* [[囊蹄蝠|囊蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros doriae'' (Borneo roundleaf bat)
* [[達雅蹄蝠|達雅蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros dyacorum'' (Dayak roundleaf bat)
* [[乌灰蹄蝠|乌灰蹄蝠]] (煤黑蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros fuliginosus'' (Sooty roundleaf bat)
* [[大耳蹄蝠|大耳蹄蝠]] (茶黃蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros fulvus'' (Fulvus roundleaf bat)
* [[黄褐蹄蝠|黄褐蹄蝠]] (短耳蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros galeritus'' (Cantor's roundleaf bat)
* [[华富里蹄蝠|华富里蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros halophyllus'' (Thailand roundleaf bat)
* [[毛冠蹄蝠|毛冠蹄蝠]] (蘇北蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros inexpectatus'' (Crested roundleaf bat)
* [[西非蹄蝠|西非蹄蝠]] (鍾思蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros jonesi'' (Jones's roundleaf bat)
* [[拉氏蹄蝠|拉氏蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros lamottei'' (Lamotte's roundleaf bat)
* [[印度蹄蝠|印度蹄蝠]] (蘭卡蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros lankadiva'' (Indian roundleaf bat)
* [[中蹄蝠|中蹄蝠]] (花面蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros larvatus'' (Intermediate roundleaf bat)
* [[泰国蹄蝠|泰国蹄蝠]] (列氏蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros lekaguli'' (Large Asian roundleaf bat)
* [[鞘面蹄蝠|鞘面蹄蝠]] (盾面蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros lylei'' (Shield-faced roundleaf bat)
* [[大泡蹄蝠|大泡蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros macrobullatus'' (Big-eared roundleaf bat)
* [[史氏蹄蝠|史氏蹄蝠]] (瑪吉蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros maggietaylarae'' (Maggie Taylor's roundleaf bat)
* [[几内亚蹄蝠|几内亚蹄蝠]] (瑪麗薩蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros marisae'' (Aellen's roundleaf bat)
* [[串耳蹄蝠|串耳蹄蝠]] (大耳蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros megalotis'' (Ethiopian large-eared roundleaf bat)
* [[长耳蹄蝠|长耳蹄蝠]] (伏河蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros muscinus'' (Fly river roundleaf bat)
* [[楔缝蹄蝠|楔缝蹄蝠]] (馬來蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros nequarii'' (Malayan roundleaf bat)
* [[暗色蹄蝠|暗色蹄蝠]] (陰暗蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros obscura'' (Philippine forest roundleaf bat)
* [[巴布亞蹄蝠|巴布亞蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros papua'' (Biak roundleaf bat)
* [[果树蹄蝠|果树蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros pomona'' (Pomona roundleaf bat)
* [[普氏蹄蝠|普氏蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros pratti'' (Pratt's roundleaf bat)
* [[吕宋蹄蝠|吕宋蹄蝠]] (微型蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros pygmaeus'' (Philippine pygmy roundleaf bat)
* [[雷氏蹄蝠|雷氏蹄蝠]] (里氏蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros ridleyi'' (Ridley's roundleaf bat)
* [[赤道蹄蝠|赤道蹄蝠]] (赤色蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros ruber'' (Noack's roundleaf bat)
* [[沙巴蹄蝠|沙巴蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros sabanus'' (Least roundleaf bat)
* [[裂蹄蝠|裂蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros schistaceus'' (Split roundleaf bat)
* [[扁吻蹄蝠|扁吻蹄蝠]] (大疣鼻蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros semoni'' (Semon's roundleaf bat)
* [[施氏蹄蝠|施氏蹄蝠]] (穴蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros speoris'' (Schneider's roundleaf bat)
* [[狭耳蹄蝠|狭耳蹄蝠]] (狹耳蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros stenotis'' (Narrow-eared roundleaf bat)
* [[丑蹄蝠|丑蹄蝠]] - ''Hipposideros turpis'' (lesser roundleaf bat)
* [[沃氏蹄蝠|沃氏蹄蝠]] (烏氏蹄蝠) - ''Hipposideros wallastoni'' (Wollaston's roundleaf bat)
* [[安達曼馬蹄蝠|安達曼馬蹄蝠]]

